-- British Open Golf Play Suspended by Darkness With Second Round Unfinished
-- Larry Siddons
-- 2010-07-16T20:49:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-16/british-open-golf-play-suspended-by-darkness-with-second-round-unfinished.html

          
          
             Play has been suspended by darkness
at the British Open with the second round unfinished. Golfers
are able to finish the hole they are playing, then must return
tomorrow to complete their rounds at the Old Course in St.
Andrews, Scotland.  
          
          


  


        